<%# The React subtree owns navigation under /tanstack_starter. Scope Turbo off
    this boundary (data-turbo="false") so Turbo Drive and TanStack Router never
    compete for the same link clicks. See issue #3485 for the open
    Turbo-coexistence track. -%>
